description: Kingfisher plc, together with its subsidiaries, supplies home improvement products and services primarily in the United Kingdom, Ireland, France, and internationally. The company also offers property investment, finance, digital, sourcing and franchising, and IT services. It operates approximately 1,470 stores in eight countries across Europe under the B&Q, Castorama, Brico Dépôt, Screwfix, TradePoint, and Koctas brands. The company provides its products through various channels, such as home improvement specialist stores and e-commerce. Kingfisher plc was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.
